author: pats
msg: Initial check-in of annotated bibliography files, with comments on only one paper.
raw_bibliography.bib contains bibtex citations, annotated_bibliography.tex uses it as the
bibliography file for a document that discusses the papers. annotated_bibliography.pdf is the
derived pdf file. It is checked in, despite being a derived file, to make the document available
through svn without requiring installation of latex and bibtex processing.
